	<article class="post-627972 post type-post status-publish hentry category-financial-services category-legal tag-bank-of-england tag-banking-and-financial-institutions tag-bp-plc tag-carney-mark-j tag-great-britain tag-lloyds-banking-group-plc tag-osborne-george tag-referendums tag-royal-bank-of-scotland-plc-2 tag-scotland tag-van-beurden-ben per-carney-mark-j per-osborne-george per-van-beurden-ben des-banking-and-financial-institutions des-referendums org-bank-of-england org-bp-plc org-lloyds-banking-group-plc org-royal-bank-of-scotland-plc geo-great-britain geo-scotland news_keywords-bank-of-england news_keywords-banking-and-finance news_keywords-ben-van-beurden news_keywords-george-osborne news_keywords-great-britain news_keywords-mark-carney news_keywords-referendum news_keywords-royal-bank-of-scotland news_keywords-scotland" id="post-627972">
	<header class="postHeader">
